<http://example.org/eudamed-ontology> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Ontology> .
<http://example.org/eudamed-ontology> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/abstract> "MedDevOnt provides a formal semantic representation of the EUDAMED catalogue, covering medical devices, manufacturers, risks, incidents and field safety corrective actions" .
<http://example.org/eudamed-ontology> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/created> "2026-04-27" .
<http://example.org/eudamed-ontology> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/creator> "Laura Palau" .
<http://example.org/eudamed-ontology> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "An ontology modelling the European catalogue of high-risk medical devices and in vitro diagnostic devices under MDR (EU 2017/745) and IVDR (EU 2017/746)." .
<http://example.org/eudamed-ontology> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/license> <https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/> .
<http://example.org/eudamed-ontology> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/modified> "2026-04-27" .
<http://example.org/eudamed-ontology> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/publisher> "Universitat Oberta de Catalunya (UOC)" .
<http://example.org/eudamed-ontology> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/rights> "This ontology is distributed under a Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International License." .
<http://example.org/eudamed-ontology> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "MedDevOnt - European Medical Device Catalogue Ontology" .
<http://example.org/eudamed-ontology> <http://purl.org/vocab/vann/preferredNamespacePrefix> "eudamed" .
<http://example.org/eudamed-ontology> <http://purl.org/vocab/vann/preferredNamespaceUri> "http://example.org/eudamed-ontology#" .
<http://example.org/eudamed-ontology> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "MedDevOnt" .
<http://example.org/eudamed-ontology> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#versionIRI> "http://example.org/eudamed-ontology/1.0" .
<http://example.org/eudamed-ontology> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#versionInfo> "1.0" .
